OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1775740267
OL,3,CKent Police should 'expand independent
OL,4,Cscrutiny of stop-and-search' incidents
OL,6,FKent Police should "expand independent
OL,7,Fscrutiny of stop-and-search"
OL,8,Fincidents, according to inspectors.
OL,10,FHis Majesty's Inspectorate of
OL,11,FConstabulary and Fire & Rescue
OL,12,FServices (HMICFRS) found that an
OL,13,Findependent panel - made up of public
OL,14,Fvolunteers - for reviewing the force's
OL,15,Fbody-worn video had seen only 11 cases
OL,16,Fin a year.
OL,18,FHMICFRS said there was an
OL,19,F"insufficient level of independent
OL,20,Fscrutiny" which "limits the
OL,21,Fopportunity" for feedback.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1775740267
OL,3,CKent Police should 'expand independent
OL,4,Cscrutiny of stop-and-search' incidents
OL,6,FThe report also found that in 14 of 20
OL,7,Fcases reviewed, the documents provided
OL,8,Fdidn't contain sufficient detail or
OL,9,Frationale to justify why the officers
OL,10,Fhad used force, the level of force or
OL,11,Fthe specific tactic used against an
OL,12,Findividual.
OL,14,FThe inspectorate said Kent Police
OL,15,Facknowledged the issue and planned to
OL,16,Fintroduce an automated reminder in
OL,17,Fearly 2026 to prompt officers to
OL,18,Frecord their rationale.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1775740267
OL,3,CKent Police should 'expand independent
OL,4,Cscrutiny of stop-and-search' incidents
OL,6,FOverall, HMICFRS graded Kent Police as
OL,7,F"adequate" in five aspects of
OL,8,Fpolicing, "good" in two and
OL,9,F"outstanding" in one.
OL,11,FRoy Wilsher OBE QFSM, His Majesty's
OL,12,FInspector of Constabulary said: "I am
OL,13,Fpleased with several aspects of the
OL,14,Fperformance of Kent Police in keeping
OL,15,Fpeople safe, reducing crime and giving
OL,16,Fvictims an effective service.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1775740267
OL,3,CKent Police should 'expand independent
OL,4,Cscrutiny of stop-and-search' incidents
OL,6,F"Since our last inspection, the force
OL,7,Fhas improved how it attracts, develops
OL,8,Fand retains its workforce. It has also
OL,9,Fstrengthened how it responds to the
OL,10,Fpublic and investigates crime.
OL,12,F"However, I have identified areas the
OL,13,Fforce should continue to focus on,
OL,14,Fincluding how it records and reviews
OL,15,Fits use of police powers and how it
OL,16,Fprotects people who are at risk of
OL,17,Fharm.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1775740267
OL,3,CKent Police should 'expand independent
OL,4,Cscrutiny of stop-and-search' incidents
OL,6,F"Officers use body-worn video
OL,7,Feffectively, and the force is testing
OL,8,Flive-streaming technology. Training
OL,9,Fand feedback help officers improve how
OL,10,Fthey use stop and search and use of
OL,11,Fforce powers. However, the force
OL,12,Fshould make sure that officers record
OL,13,Fclear reasons when they use force. It
OL,14,Fmust also expand independent scrutiny
OL,15,Fof both stop and search and use of
OL,16,Fforce.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1775740267
OL,3,CKent Police should 'expand independent
OL,4,Cscrutiny of stop-and-search' incidents
OL,6,F"...I am optimistic that Kent Police
OL,7,Fwill continue to make improvements. I
OL,8,Fhave given the force specific
OL,9,Frecommendations that set out the areas
OL,10,Fit needs to focus on, and I will
OL,11,Fcontinue to monitor performance."
OL,13,FDeputy Chief Constable of Kent Police,
OL,14,FPeter Ayling, said: "We welcome the
OL,15,Ffindings of the 2025-27 PEEL
OL,16,Fassessment which should give the
OL,17,Fpublic of Kent confidence in our
OL,18,Fcommitment to supporting and
OL,19,Fprotecting victims, catching
OL,20,Fcriminals, and solving crime.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1775740267
OL,3,CKent Police should 'expand independent
OL,4,Cscrutiny of stop-and-search' incidents
OL,6,F"The independent policing inspectorate
OL,7,Fhighlighted many examples of good
OL,8,Fpractice, especially in regard to the
OL,9,Fway we prevent and deter crime.
OL,11,F"The hard work and professionalism of
OL,12,Four officers and staff is recognised
OL,13,Fby the fact that Kent Police is one of
OL,14,Fa very small number of forces where
OL,15,Fnot a single area was found to be
OL,16,Finadequate, and we are meeting or
OL,17,Fexceeding the standard in all areas.
OL,19,F"I'm incredibly proud of their
OL,20,Fdedication to protect and serve the
OL,21,Fpeople of Kent 24/7.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1775740267
OL,3,CKent Police should 'expand independent
OL,4,Cscrutiny of stop-and-search' incidents
OL,6,F"We will, however, not be complacent
OL,7,Fand are already focused on areas we
OL,8,Fcan improve to ensure we provide the
OL,9,Fbest service possible to our
OL,10,Fcommunities."
OL,12,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,13,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,14,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,15,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,16,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,17,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/8
